response.original_title: The new year that became cheesy.
response.overview: A group of 4 friends that all secretly despise each other come together on new years eve and do the annual "eating grapes under the table to make your wishes come true at midnight" tradition. But they don't exactly have grapes, so they use Cheetos instead. One of the girls in particular makes dark wishes upon the other girls and it comes to them quick.
response.tagline: "Be careful what you wish for, it comes to you fast."
response.title: The new year that became cheesy.
